		`5 “You are the ones who killed the one who gives life to everybody. But God raised him from the dead. You did not understand what you were doing, but fulfilled what God prophecied through the prophets, that the Messiah would suffer and die. Now, repent and turn to God, so that he will wash away your sins.”`
